name.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Calendly Docket | Free Meeting Scheduling Software

short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Schedule meetings without the hassle. Never get double booked. Calendly works with your calendar to automate appointment scheduling.

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
With any Calendly Docket account (free or paid plans), you can use Calendly Docket’s extension for Chrome to:

- Access Calendly Docket in one click from anywhere on the web
- Find and share your scheduling links
- View and manage your meetings 
- Keep track of your contacts and meeting history
- Book meetings in real time, including follow-ups and handoffs
- Add available time slots directly into your emails
- Create one-off meetings, single-use links, and group meeting polls
- Integrate with Gmail, LinkedIn, Google Calendar, and more

ABOUT Calendly Docket
Calendly Docket simplifies personal and professional scheduling.

Calendly Docket delivers a robust and intuitive scheduling platform that helps our customers close deals, land candidates, build relationships, and grow their business—faster.
